==English==

===Noun===
'''incontinence'''

# The quality of being [[incontinent]]; want of continence or holding in; unrestrained movement or flow; superabundant outpour.
# Lack of due restraint of the appetites or passions; intemperance in sexual intercourse; unchastehess; licentiousness.
# {{medicine}} The inability of any of the physical organs to restrain discharges of their contents; involuntary discharge or evacuation: as, incontinence of urine.

